v><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Switch to dark mode\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8 theme-toggle\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"md:hidden\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8 mobile-nav\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><article class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><header class=\"mb-10 space-y-4\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif sm:text-5xl\">Why I Started Appropriated Kitchen</h1><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>June 12, 2026</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>1 min read</span><span class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-muted text-muted-foreground\">personal</span><span class=\"text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-muted text-muted-foreground\">behind-the-scenes</span></span></div></header><div class=\"prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-lg prose-headings:font-serif prose-headings:text-2xl prose-headings:mt-10 prose-headings:mb-4 prose-a:text-primary prose-img:rounded-xl prose-li:marker:text-primary\"><p>Every great kitchen has a story. This one starts with a question: <strong>why do we cook the way we do?</strong></p>\n<p>I grew up in a house where food was love. My grandmother never used a recipe — she cooked by feel, by taste, by memory. A pinch of this, a handful of that, and somehow it was always perfect. When I asked her how she did it, she&#x27;d smile and say, &quot;That&#x27;s <em>my</em> way.&quot;</p>\n<p>Years later, living in my own apartment with a tiny kitchen and even tinier budget, I realized something. The recipes I was finding online were either:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Overcomplicated (13 ingredients for Tuesday night dinner? No thanks.)</li>\n<li>Watered down (where&#x27;s the flavor?)</li>\n<li>Gatekept behind &quot;secret&quot; techniques</li>\n</ol>\n<p>So I started doing what my grandmother did — taking the food I loved and making it <em>my way</em>.</p>\n<h2>The Philosophy</h2>\n<p><strong>Appropriated Kitchen</strong> isn&#x27;t about cultural appropriation — it&#x27;s about <em>culinary appreciation</em>. It&#x27;s the belief that great food belongs to everyone, and that the best recipes are the ones you make your own.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Take what you love.</strong> Find dishes that excite you.</li>\n<li><strong>Learn the why.</strong> Understand the technique, not just the steps.</li>\n<li><strong>Make it yours.</strong> Adjust, experiment, break the rules.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>What to Expect</h2>\n<p>This blog will have:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Recipes</strong> that are tested, photographed, and written with personality</li>\n<li><strong>Nutritional info</strong> for every recipe (because eating well matters)</li>\n<li><strong>Printable recipe cards</strong> so you can cook without scrolling</li>\n<li><strong>Honest opinions</strong> about what worked, what didn&#x27;t, and what I&#x27;d change next time</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Your Food, My Way</h2>\n<p>That&#x27;s not just a tagline. It&#x27;s an invitation. Take these recipes, make them your own, and let me know how it goes.</p>\n<p>Welcome to the kitchen.</p></div></article><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><a class=\"text-lg font-bold font-serif\" href=\"/\">Appropriated Kitchen</a><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground italic\">Your Food, My Way</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/appropriatedkitchen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"Instagram\" class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.