she did it, she'd smile and say, \\\"That's \",[\"$\",\"em\",\"em-0\",{\"children\":\"my\"}],\" way.\\\"\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-2\",{\"children\":\"Years later, living in my own apartment with a tiny kitchen and even tinier budget, I realized something. The recipes I was finding online were either:\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",\"ol-0\",{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-0\",{\"children\":\"Overcomplicated (13 ingredients for Tuesday night dinner? No thanks.)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-1\",{\"children\":\"Watered down (where's the flavor?)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-2\",{\"children\":\"Gatekept behind \\\"secret\\\" techniques\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-3\",{\"children\":[\"So I started doing what my grandmother did — taking the food I loved and making it \",[\"$\",\"em\",\"em-0\",{\"children\":\"my way\"}],\".\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",\"h2-0\",{\"children\":\"The Philosophy\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-4\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Appropriated Kitchen\"}],\" isn't about cultural appropriation — it's about \",[\"$\",\"em\",\"em-0\",{\"children\":\"culinary appreciation\"}],\". It's the belief that great food belongs to everyone, and that the best recipes are the ones you make your own.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",\"ul-0\",{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-0\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Take what you love.\"}],\" Find dishes that excite you.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-1\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Learn the why.\"}],\" Understand the technique, not just the steps.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-2\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Make it yours.\"}],\" Adjust, experiment, break the rules.\"]}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",\"h2-1\",{\"children\":\"What to Expect\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-5\",{\"children\":\"This blog will have:\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",\"ul-1\",{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-0\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Recipes\"}],\" that are tested, photographed, and written with personality\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-1\",{\"children\":[\"$L1e\",\" for every recipe (because eating well matters)\"]}],\"\\n\",\"$L1f\",\"\\n\",\"$L20\",\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",\"$L21\",\"\\n\",\"$L22\",\"\\n\",\"$L23\"]}]]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Nutritional info\"}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-2\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Printable recipe cards\"}],\" so you can cook without scrolling\"]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"li\",\"li-3\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",\"strong-0\",{\"children\":\"Honest opinions\"}],\" about what worked, what didn't, and what I'd change next time\"]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"h2\",\"h2-2\",{\"children\":\"Your Food, My Way\"}]\n22:[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-6\",{\"children\":\"That's not just a tagline. It's an invitation. Take these recipes, make them your own, and let me know how it goes.\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-7\",{\"children\":\"Welcome to the kitchen.\"}]\n1a:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n24:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/2l23laejyscle.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0i31m7nnsmowg.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n17:null\n1c:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Why I Started Appropriated Kitchen | Appropriated Kitchen\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"The story behind the blog and what 'Your Food, My Way' really means — a manifesto of sorts.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Why I Started Appropriated Kitchen\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"The story behind the blog and what 'Your Food, My Way' really means — a manifesto of sorts.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:type\",\"content\":\"article